432402,"uid":44909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"你估如果我講到瞓唔到/唔夠瞓，入到去我鋪頭實放鬆到得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n佢覺得瞓左放鬆就去瞓，篤場波放鬆到就去隔離動篤場波<br />\n<br />\n間開房個邊就收貴啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a76a26aab2d58caeb0350d04b22ffbfaf51d3d","tid":432402,"uid":44909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根據《旅館業條例》（第349章），任何人在未領有牌照或豁免證明書下經營、開設、管理或以其他方式控制旅館（每次出租的最短租出期為連續28天者除外）（無牌經營旅館），一經定罪，最高可處罰款200,000元及監禁兩年，並可就罪行持續期間的每一天另處罰款20,000元。近年有不少無牌旅館透過網上平台招徠。<br />\n<br />\n利申:純google</blockquote><br />\n點先計旅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8bdf386f2ddd60a6de9b8117c5cb37dfa54dc4","tid":432402,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"之前咪有人係中環開左，比office人入去訓陣<br />\n好似都比人當旅館咁charge"},{"pid":"a1a1ceef06b0f34198cc780e2f4fc7ab44b408fb","tid":432402,"uid":52576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E5%91%A8%E5%88%8A%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E9%80%9A/article/20161103/2_17777001/90%E5%BE%8C%E5%89%B5%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E9%96%93-%E6%94%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD%E6%97%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2588%258A%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2580%259A%2Farticle%2F20161103%2F2_17777001%2F90%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%2588%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%2581%25AF%25E9%2596%2593-%25E6%2594%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%2597%258F&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=913c0778\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2588%258A%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2580%259A%2Farticle%2F20161